<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><strong>What could be more enticing and relaxing than exploring a country from the comfort of a luxurious floating hotel? We are delighted to offer this luxurious Classical Rhine river cruise, on one of Europe's most beautiful and interesting waterways. Discover the incredible diversity of the Rhine and enjoy excellent service and hospitality on board the elegant Amadeus ships. During your scenic journey, indulge in classic local dishes and wine from Europe's great wine regions, take optional guided sightseeing tours on shore or explore on your own by bike or on foot.</strong></p>
<div style="position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/GWIZ4uKKRqU?rel=0&amp;showinfo=0" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="349" width="560"></iframe></div>
<p>Enjoy an unforgettable 8 day river cruise along the Rhine, through Switzerland, France, Germany and the Netherlands. Journey past picturesque landscapes and vineyards in the beautiful Rhine valley and past lively cities and quaint medieval towns and castles. Explore vivid Amsterdam where you can cruise along its historic canals and visit countless sights and attractions. This cruise is available in either direction (Basel-Amsterdam &amp; Amsterdam-Basel) on selected dates.</p>
<p><strong>Basel-Amsterdam:</strong><br />14th May 2015 (AMADEUS Silver II)<br />18th September 2015 (AMADEUS Princess)</p>
<p><strong>Amsterdam-Basel: </strong></p>
<p><strong>21st May 2015 (AMADEUS Silver II)   NEW DATE FROM £949<br /></strong>4th June 2015 (AMADEUS Silver II) <br />18th June 2015 (AMADEUS Silver II) <br />25th June 2015 (AMADEUS Brilliant)<br />31st July 2015 (AMADEUS Princess)</p>
</div>
