<h2 class="geolocation-title location-text">Life on Board</h2>
<p>You are invited on an unforgettable journey along the Rhine, with the AMADEUS fleet of luxury cruisers. The tastefully furnished ships  (AMADEUS Princess, Brilliant, and its flagship AMADEUS Silver II) stand out for their modern elegance, exceptional spaciousness and relaxed atmosphere. They are luxurious floating hotels and you can expect superb service and hospitality from an experienced English speaking tour manager and a friendly crew. </p>
<h3><strong>Cabins</strong></h3>
<ul>
<li>70-80</li>
<li>All tastefully furnished cabins are outside facing and have seating area and en suite shower, wc</li>
<li>Haydn cabins on the lower deck have windows (do not open)</li>
<li>Strauss cabins on the middle deck and Mozart cabins on the upper level have large French balconies</li>
<li>Larger Mozart Suites on the upper level are available on request.</li>
<li>All cabins are air-conditioned and equipped with TV, telephone, safe and hairdryer and are also available for single occupancy</li>
<li>Beds can be separated if required</li>
</ul>
